scriptmanager.objects

Class ToolDescriptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • scriptmanager.objects.ToolDescriptions

  • public class ToolDescriptions
extends java.lang.Object
    This class acts as a central and shared storage location for each tool's description for consistentcy betweeen CLI help message and the GUI-displayed text.
    Author:
    Olivia Lang
    See Also:
    ScriptManager, ScriptManagerGUI, scriptmanager.cli.BAM_Format_Converter, scriptmanager.cli.BAM_Statistics, scriptmanager.cli.Coordinate_Manipulation, scriptmanager.cli.Figure_Generation, scriptmanager.cli.File_Utilities, scriptmanager.cli.Peak_Analysis, scriptmanager.cli.Peak_Calling, scriptmanager.cli.Read_Analysis, scriptmanager.cli.Sequence_Analysis
